Subject: [PATCH] TRSE API: CoCo/Dragon output_type=bin, INI merge, strip #
 comments

- compile.php: strip # lines from trse.ini; merge trse.defaults.ini (assembler_6809=OrgAsm);
  force output_type=bin for TRS80COCO/DRAGON; include .bin in artifacts
- trse.defaults.ini: OrgAsm for 6809
- README: document host behavior; clarify IDE vs server for CoCo bin
